{"lemma":"زُرُق","slug":"زُرُق","root":"ز.ر.ق","root_slug":"ز-ر-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ر-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"زُرُق","root":"زرق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17685","n17686","n17689","n17696"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%8F%D9%82"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"flickering, glinting","tags":["obsolete"],"examples":[{"text":"وَنَحْشُرُ الْمُجْرِمِينَ يَوْمَئِذٍ زُرْقًا","english":"We will gather the delinquents that day [with their eyes] glinting [from fear]."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"blue, blue-coloured"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Color or defect adjective from the root ز ر ق (z r q). Compare Ancient Greek γλαυκός (glaukós) for the semantic development.\n\nSee the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":["/ʔaz.raq/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17685","headword_ar":"زَرِقَ","root":"zrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (MA, TA,) [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraqN","text_ar":"زَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, MA, KL, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuroqapN","text_ar":"زُرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA,) [or the latter is a simple subst.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had that colour of the eye which is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuroqap","text_ar":"زُرْقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; (S, TA;) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was blue-eyed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gray-eyed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, PS;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a greenish hue in the eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so I render the Pers. explanation"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sbz J$m $d","text_ar":"سبز چشم شد"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (MA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zariqato Eayonuhu","text_ar":"زَرِقَتْ عَيْنُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayonuhu","text_ar":"عَيْنُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Azrq~t","text_ar":"ازرقّت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AizoriqaAqN","text_ar":"اِزْرِقَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayonuhu","text_ar":"عَيْنُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AzrAq~t","text_ar":"ازراقّت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AizoriyqaAqN","text_ar":"اِزْرِيقَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His eye was of the colour termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuroqapN","text_ar":"زُرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his eye was gray;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA;) [&c.] ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zariqa","text_ar":"زَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraqN","text_ar":"زَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, TK)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, blind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TK.) ―         -b3-  [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zariqa Aln~aSolu","text_ar":"زَرِقَ النَّصْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraqN","text_ar":"زَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is app. used as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The iron head or blade"},{"kind":"text","text":"of an arrow &c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, very clear"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bright:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraqN","text_ar":"زَرَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.] ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zariqa AlmaA='u","text_ar":"زَرِقَ المَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The water was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, clear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Azrq~","text_ar":"ازرقّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraqato Eayonuhu naHowiY","text_ar":"زَرَقَتْ عَيْنُهُ نَحْوِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His eye turned towards me so that the white thereof appeared;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azoraqato","text_ar":"اَزْرَقَتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aizoraq~ato","text_ar":"اِزْرَقَّتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Fr, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraqahu","text_ar":"زَرَقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraqahu bimizoraAqK","text_ar":"زَرَقَهُ بِمِزْرَاقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"birumoHK","text_ar":"بِرُمْحٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaroqN","text_ar":"زَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cast at him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he thrust him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pierced him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mzrAq","text_ar":"مزراق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"javelin"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, Mgh, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a spear."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraqahu biEayonihi","text_ar":"زَرَقَهُ بِعَيْنِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bibaSarihi","text_ar":"بِبَصَرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He looked sharply,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intently,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attentively, at him; he cast his eye at him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraqati Alr~aHola","text_ar":"زَرَقَتِ الرَّحْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHimola","text_ar":"الحِمْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made the saddle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the load,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to shift backwards:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimolahaA","text_ar":"حِمْلَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azoraqato","text_ar":"اَزْرَقَتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_izoraAqN","text_ar":"اـِزْرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made her load to shift backwards."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) [See also 2.]       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraqa","text_ar":"زَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaroqN","text_ar":"زَرْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) said of a bird,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araqa","text_ar":"ذَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It muted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dunged"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, Msb, K.)"}],"source_refs":["MA","TA","S","KL","TK","K","Mgh","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n17686","headword_ar":"زرّق","root":"zrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to Golius, as on the authority of the KL, “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"Pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"JkAnyd","text_ar":"چكانيد"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fecit ut stillaret, stillatim emisit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"” but it appears from my copy of the KL that this should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zh~q","text_ar":"زهّق"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for I there find"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazohiyqN","text_ar":"تَزْهِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazoriyqN","text_ar":"تَزْرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":") expl. by the Pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"JkAnydn","text_ar":"چكانيدن"},{"kind":"text","text":": then, however, immediately follows, in that copy, another explanation: ―         -b2-  and The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shifting backwards of a camel's saddle from his back:"},{"kind":"text","text":"therefore it seems that either"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazoriyqN","text_ar":"تَزْرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is there omitted before this second explanation, (see 1, last sentence but one, and see 7,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazohiyqN","text_ar":"تَزْهِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is there a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazoriyqN","text_ar":"تَزْرِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17689","headword_ar":"زَرَقٌ","root":"zrq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zariqa","text_ar":"زَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.: and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuroqapN","text_ar":"زُرْقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Blindness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) in this sense also an inf. n. of which the verb is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zariqa","text_ar":"زَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TK.) ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quality of being very clear"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bright,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the iron head or blade of an arrow &c. (ISk, S. [See, again"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zariqa","text_ar":"زَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which it is app., in this sense likewise, an inf. n.]) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sort of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHojiyl","text_ar":"تَحْجِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness in the legs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in three of the legs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the two kind legs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in one kind leg, beneath the knees and hocks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneath the hocks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneath the hock, of a horse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not including the border of the pastern next the hoof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AO, K:) or, as some say, (TA, but in the K “ and ”)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a whiteness not surrounding the bone altogether, but"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"only"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a whiteness of the hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaHN","text_ar":"وَضَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon a part thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","AO"]},{"entry_id":"n17696","headword_ar":"زُرَّقٌ","root":"zrq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain bird used for catching other birds;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species of hawk called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAziY","text_ar":"بَازِى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baA$aq","text_ar":"بَاشَق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sparrow-hawk"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (IDrd, TA:) or, accord. to Fr, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAziY","text_ar":"بَازِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"falcon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, TA:) [but] it is said in the A,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yuqaAsu Alz~ur~aqu biAlA^azoraqi","text_ar":"لَا يُقَاسُ الزُّرَّقُ بِالاَزْرَقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zur~aq","text_ar":"زُرَّق"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is not to be compared with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azoraq","text_ar":"اَزْرَق"},{"kind":"text","text":"], which latter is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAzY","text_ar":"بازى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaraAriyqu","text_ar":"زَرَارِيقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A whiteness in the forelock of a horse;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the hinder part of his head, behind the forelock."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Some white hairs in the fore leg of a horse;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his hind leg."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sharp-sighted:"},{"kind":"text","text":"mentioned by Sb, and expl. by Seer. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["IDrd","TA","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}